<HEADLINE>
WATER AT HEART OF TURKEY'S POLICIES ON KURDS AND MIDEAST
NEIGHBORS 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
