dropout playing for the Job Corps Center. But after finally getting
his GED at age 25 in 1997, big-time college coaches know about
Lyons now. He is averaging 27 points _ best in the nation among
junior college players _ for nationally ranked Georgia Perimeter in
metro Atlanta. FSU is among the schools recruiting the player
teammates call ``Old School.'' (Curtright, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
