her routine on the uneven bars at the Southern California Acro Team
Gymnastics club (SCATS). Antolin's quest to make it onto next
year's U.S. Olympic gymnastics team is gaining momentum. She has
already achieved her goal for this year -- making it onto the
Pan-American team -- and a recent performance earned her an
unexpected invitation to the American Cup next weekend in St.
Petersburg, Fla. (Jill Connelly/New York Times Photo)
</P>
